\end_inset

 are the measures 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mu_{t_{1},\dots,t_{k}}\left(F_{1}\times F_{2}\times\cdots\times F_{k}\right)=P\left(X_{t_{1}}\in F_{1},\dots,X_{t_{k}}\in F_{k}\right)
\]

\end_inset

on 
